                <head>228. Summary of Conclusions of a Special Coordination Committee Meeting<note
                        n="1" type="source" xml:id="d228fn1">Source: Carter Library, National
                        Security Council Institutional Files, 1977–1981, Box 109, <gloss
                            target="#t_SCC_1">SCC</gloss>–284, 3/6/80, Iran &amp; Afghanistan. Top
                        Secret. The meeting took place in the White House Situation Room. In the
                        upper right corner, <persName corresp="#p_CJE_1">Carter</persName> wrote:
                        “Zbig, C.”</note>
                </head>
